Aman ɣusnin, ur ... gan ɣ txssa n [[Afgan|ufgan]] imqqurn 65 %, dar wazzan 75 %, dar ubijju n krad yirn 95 %. Gan iggii n wakal 70 % ilin gis 97 % w-aman smmumni d 3 % [[Nitrujin|N]] win mmimnin. ɣ twuriwin n takrura ar nsawal f H<sub>2</sub>O mac ɣid gan aman ɣusnin (s [[tafransist|tfransist]] : ''l'eau pure'') ur gisn mqqard kra yadnin. Gin waman yat tɣawsa lli isfzyn kraygat anaw n lmεdn niɣ aẓru.
Mac aman lli nttafa ɣ iggi n wakal ur jju iga tafga ar 100% illa bdda gis imik n tifgiwin n tɣawsiwin yaḍnin. addad itffin (''état liquide'').

